gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 129, Hawks 122
gameRecap.excerpt: Jamal Murray led the Nuggets with a season-high 29 points, nine rebounds, and four assists as the Nuggets defeated the Hawks, 129-122. Nikola Jokic (25 points, eight rebounds, eight assists) and Julian Strawther (career-high 22 points, and career-high six 3PT FG) added 47 points. Bogdan Bogdanovic led the Hawks with a career-high 40 points and knocked down a career-high 10-17 from the beyond the arc. The Nuggets snapped a 3-game losing streak and move to 15-9 as the Hawks fall to 9-13.
